        "order": 8
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_exam_paper_en-file-putnam-archive_1997_Problems_1997_page_001_13",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "B–4 Let am,n denote the coefficient of xn in the expansion of (1 + x + x2)m. Prove that for all [integers] k ≥ 0,",
